msgid "|Scale of Map |Map Horizontal Accuracy (http://www.ga.gov.au/mapspecs/topographic/v5/index.html[Geoscience Australia^]) |Map Horizontal Accuracy (https://pubs.usgs.gov/fs/1999/0171/report.pdf[USGS^]) |NSSDA Horizontal Accuracy (https://www.fgdc.gov/standards/projects/accuracy/part3/chapter3[FGDC 1998^])\n"
